def load_dist(sysname, pathname):
    basedir = '../../2.datasets/1.merge_ds/raw_ds'
    ds = numpy.load(f'{basedir}/{sysname}.{pathname}.raw_x.npy')
    lb = numpy.load(f'{basedir}/{sysname}.{pathname}.raw_xlbl.npy')
    # if sysname == 'toho_amp': print(lb)
    return numpy.asarray([ds[i*50,:] for i in range(200)]), lb

# R1AE =======================
# 'AMP.285.N4:AMP.285.C7' : 31
# 'SER.69.OG:AMP.285.C7'  : 52
# 'LYS.72.NZ:SER.69.OG'   : 54
# 'SER.129.OG:AMP.285.N4' : 61
# 'LYS.72.NZ:SER.129.OG'  : 62
# R2AE =======================
# 'AMP.285.N4:AMP.285.C7' : 28
# 'SER.69.OG:AMP.285.C7'  : 49
# 'LYS.72.NZ:SER.69.OG'   : 51
# 'SER.129.OG:AMP.285.N4' : 58
# 'LYS.72.NZ:SER.129.OG'  : 59

pathname = 'r1ae'
amp_sel = [52, 31, 59, 53, 62, 61] if pathname == 'r1ae' else [49, 28, 59, 58, 51]
xticks = ['Bond-0\n(B0)', 'Bond-1\n(B1)', 'Bond-2\n(P0)', 'Bond-3\n(P1)', 'Bond-4\n(P2)', 'Bond-5\n(P3)'] if pathname == 'r1ae' else \
         ['Bond-0\n(B0)', 'Bond-1\n(B1)', 'Bond-4\n(P2)', 'Bond-5\n(P3)', 'Bond-6\n(P4)']

amp_keydist, lbl = load_dist('toho_amp', pathname)
print(lbl[amp_sel])
cex_sel = amp_sel
cex_keydist, lbl = load_dist('toho_cex', pathname)

print(lbl[cex_sel])
# init figure ==================================================================
sns.set_style(style='white')
sns.set_style("ticks")
fig, ax,  = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 5.5), dpi=900, facecolor='w', edgecolor='k', )
plt.subplots_adjust(left=1.5/8, right=7.5/8, top=5/5.5, bottom=1.5/5.5)
ax.tick_params(which='major', direction='in', length=6, width=1, labelsize='x-large', )

#ax.set_xlim(0, 100)
ax.set_ylim(1.0, 5.0)
#plt.yticks([5*y for y in range(5)])
ax.text(0.02, 0.96,'Toho/AMP: '+pathname[:2].upper()+'-'+pathname[2:].upper(),
        ha='left', va='top', transform=ax.transAxes, fontsize=18, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[0])
ax.text(0.98, 0.96,'Toho/CEX: '+pathname[:2].upper()+'-'+pathname[2:].upper(),
        ha='right', va='top', transform=ax.transAxes, fontsize=18, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[1])

ax.set_ylabel(r'Distances ($\AA$)', fontsize='xx-large', )
ax.set_xlabel('Bonds\n(Chemical Processes)', fontsize='xx-large', )
ax.tick_params(labelsize='x-large')

x = numpy.arange(len(amp_sel))
amp_y = amp_keydist[:, amp_sel]
cex_y = cex_keydist[:, cex_sel]

amp_boxes = ax.boxplot(x=amp_y, positions=x-0.12, widths=0.2, showcaps=False, showfliers=False, medianprops=dict(color='k'), patch_artist=True) 
cex_boxes = ax.boxplot(x=cex_y, positions=x+0.12, widths=0.2, showcaps=False, showfliers=False, medianprops=dict(color='k'), patch_artist=True) 

for i in range(amp_y.shape[1]):
    ax.scatter(x=numpy.random.normal(loc=x[i]-0.12, scale=0.03, size=200),
           y=amp_y[:, i], s=0.1, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[0])
for i in range(cex_y.shape[1]):
    ax.scatter(x=numpy.random.normal(loc=x[i]+0.12, scale=0.03, size=200),
           y=cex_y[:, i], s=0.1, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[1])

plt.setp(amp_boxes["boxes"], facecolor='#00000000')
plt.setp(cex_boxes["boxes"], facecolor='#00000000')

plt.xticks(numpy.arange(len(amp_sel)), rotation=0)
ax.set_xticklabels(xticks)

fig.savefig('both_{0}.keydist.png'.format(pathname, ))
plt.show()

def load_dist():
    basedir = '../../2.datasets/0.mk_ds/valid_toho_cex_r2ae'
    ds = numpy.load(f'{basedir}/toho_cex.r2ae.rxc_distmat.npy')
    lb = numpy.load(f'{basedir}/toho_cex.r2ae.rxc_distlabel.npy')
    # if sysname == 'toho_amp': print(lb)
    return ds, lb

# load dftb data ================================================================

# ['SER.69.HG1:TIP3.433.OH2' 'SER.69.HG1:SER.69.OG'
#  'TIP3.433.H2:TIP3.433.OH2' 'TIP3.433.H2:GLU.165.OE1'
#  'TIP3.433.H2:GLU.165.OE2' 'TIP3.433.H1:TIP3.433.OH2'
#  'TIP3.433.H1:GLU.165.OE1' 'TIP3.433.H1:GLU.165.OE2']

pathname = 'r2ae'
sel = [0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7]
dist, lbl = load_dist()
xticks = [f'd{i}' for i in range(8)]
print(lbl)

# init figure ==================================================================
sns.set_style(style='white')
sns.set_style("ticks")
fig, ax,  = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 5.5), dpi=900, facecolor='w', edgecolor='k', )
plt.subplots_adjust(left=1.5/8, right=7.5/8, top=5/5.5, bottom=1.5/5.5)
ax.tick_params(which='major', direction='in', length=6, width=1, labelsize='x-large', )

#ax.set_xlim(0, 100)
ax.set_ylim(0.0, 5.0)
#plt.yticks([5*y for y in range(5)])
ax.text(0.02, 0.96,'Toho/CEX: '+pathname[:2].upper()+'-'+pathname[2:].upper(),
        ha='left', va='top', transform=ax.transAxes, fontsize=18, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[1])

ax.set_ylabel(r'Distances ($\AA$)', fontsize='xx-large', )
ax.set_xlabel('Bonds', fontsize='xx-large', )
ax.tick_params(labelsize='x-large')

x = numpy.arange(len(sel))
y = dist[:, sel]
boxes = ax.boxplot(x=y, positions=x, widths=0.4, showcaps=False, showfliers=False, medianprops=dict(color='k'), patch_artist=True) 

for i in range(y.shape[1]):
    ax.scatter(x=numpy.random.normal(loc=x[i], scale=0.05, size=10000),
           y=y[:, i], s=0.1, color=sns.color_palette('colorblind')[1])

plt.setp(boxes["boxes"], facecolor='#00000000')

plt.xticks(numpy.arange(len(sel)), rotation=0)
ax.set_xticklabels(xticks)

fig.savefig('tohocex_{0}.mechdist.png'.format(pathname, ))
plt.show()
